attributes.title: Play Pals - Let's Play Cursed Halo: The Maw (Finale!)
attributes.caption:
The final episode of our Cursed Halo playthrough where Gavin and Michael find out real quick that Keyes is a level they should not be playing.
Get ready for more chaos, more outlandish Warthogs driving through the Pillar of Autumn, and more of Michael making the most out of his voice effects.
